# Bee Healthy — environment shape (no real secrets here).
#
# NOTE: The user's LLM API key is entered in-app and stored on-device (IndexedDB).
# It is NOT an environment variable and must never be committed.
#
# These are only needed once cloud sync (Supabase) is wired up in a later phase.
# Vite exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client bundle — only put PUBLIC,
# non-secret values here (the Supabase anon key is safe to ship; RLS protects data).

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
